<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-317-515  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 317 515.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Feb 7 1989 v3 n6 p18(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT MacWEEK Inc. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>New contender in font design: Fred Font provides hints, grayscale. (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Lehman, Cliff.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   AB Vista Co. (product introduction).andO;Product:   FRed Font Machine (Computer program).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionFontsDesignSoftware PackagesCompatible Hardware.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>New contender in font designandM;SAN FRANCISCO -- A new font design package that may open up Adobe PostScriptlaser printers for use with font libraries other than Adobe's made its debutat the Macworld Expo here this past month.andM;The new program, called Fred Font Machine, will compete directly withFontographer from Altsys Corp. of Plano, Texas.andP;  But Fred, according to itsdevelopers, adds a host of features missing from previous Mac font tools.andM;The program, now scheduled for release in March, is being developed by ABVista Co. of Fair Oaks, Calif.andP;  Pricing has not been finalized but will beless than $500, according to Larry Applegate, a partner in AB Vista.andM;One of Fred's most important features, Applegate said, is its ability togenerate hints that allow high-quality printing on low-resolution (300-dpi)laser printers equipped with Adobe PostScript, as well as on PostScript-clonedevices.andP;  This capability would allow users to add hints to fonts fromlibraries such as Bitstream Inc.'s MacFontware and to original fonts designedwith Fred Font Machine.andM;&quot;The desktop publishing industry is increasing pressure on the type industryfor open font formats among different typeface vendors,&quot; Applegate said.andM;&quot;Fred, with its open font format together with future developments in theindustry, will overcome Adobe's present lock on the low-resolution fontmarket.&quot;andM;Other features of Fred Font give font designers the ability to draw originalPostScript typefaces; generate and edit black-and-white, gray-scale and colorbit-mapped fonts; use gray shading to smooth the appearance of on-screenfonts (antialiasing); autotrace scanned images; edit kerning pairs, characterwidths and sidebearings in context; import and edit existing Mac fontfamilies; export character outlines and composed text in Illustrator 88,Encapsulated PostScript and PICT formats.andM;Fred also coordinates a font family's outlines, bit maps, kerning tables andfont metric information.andP;  It has a multilevel undo/redo function at auser-selectable number of levels.andM;AB Vista Co. can be reached at P.O. Box 369, Fair Oaks, Calif.andP;  95628.andP;  Thecompany said it cannot yet respond to telephone inquiries.andO;</TEXT></DOC>